{"tid":426261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰羅尼亞警察總長 被西法院控以煽動叛亂罪","createTime":"2017-10-06T12:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T09:13:45.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"388eb2be52c1a49d8e912abbbf85bd8abec71e36","tid":426261,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>加泰羅尼亞警察總長 被西法院控以煽動叛亂罪</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://prism.news/images/Untitled034_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2Fimages%2FUntitled034_JPG.jpg&h=deb04f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【稜鏡新聞訊】英國電視廣播有限公司報導，加泰羅尼亞警察總長 Josep Lluis Trapero 被指控煽動叛亂罪，即將在馬德里刑事法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n總長所屬的自治區警察被指在剛過去的10月1日公投中，未能保護西班牙國家警察執行暴力鎮壓加泰羅尼亞公示威者的任務。<br />\n<br />\n剛過去的加泰羅尼亞公投被指違反西班牙法律。<br />\n<br />\n儘管西班牙憲法法院下達暫緩開會的命令，加泰羅尼亞議會仍計劃如期在星期一召開會議。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞外務總長 Raul Romeva 接受英國電視廣播有限公司訪問時表示：「議會將會召開，並且將討論議題。西政府所有企圖阻止事情發生的行為，皆屬徒勞無功，且有反效果。」<br />\n<br />\n傳即將召會的議會將以剛過去的星期日公投為基礎宣佈加泰羅尼亞獨立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.prism.news/ShowArt_m.php?ref=20171006003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.prism.news%2FShowArt_m.php%3Fref%3D20171006003&d=rqsymna4lTNBF1zk3sksWb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a571496b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.prism.news/ShowArt_m.php?ref=20171006003</a><br />\n<br />\n唔幫班西警打市民就比人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22989779725ea0c63e99eae63bb41b509b596a42","tid":426261,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  西班牙是中國人民的老朋友"},{"pid":"c2cf4f41fbead2be5f9d4f9bf4a9f9ab15d0796b","tid":426261,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾西班牙"},{"pid":"4ffdb6d9b929c1e33f0cc155bfda7da93b5121d8","tid":426261,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":48,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"遲早香港都會變成咁<br />\n<br />\n香港警務處長, 被中國法院控以煽動叛亂罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2b38870c0256e866ce7ac924cf57441ce79d2c","tid":426261,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"英文版本？"},{"pid":"5e13d37ed8af4533bbd3602379ec689d5ee2657c","tid":426261,"uid":3659,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早香港都會變成咁<br />\n<br />\n香港警務處長, 被中國法院控以煽動叛亂罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎汽水蓋就有佢份"},{"pid":"0665255fcd683e72c2c87112a0cf9947a3b90cc5","tid":426261,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"之前咩報紙話加泰獨派勢力吹大咗，仲有好多沉默的大多數"},{"pid":"4585fe9ae5f4a6e4bbefb827cc30f4809409467b","tid":426261,"uid":4387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早香港都會變成咁<br />\n<br />\n香港警務處長, 被中國法院控以煽動叛亂罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會呀 香港班警犬邊可能咁有骨氣"},{"pid":"b3bde41c947dbe1afe9004773ac8dacfc0309e32","tid":426261,"uid":61325,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"請時刻留意回覆者的會員名稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5030a1a53efeb7bfbae5356064f1d94699d85177","tid":426261,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英文版本？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-41523250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-41523250&d=rqsymna4lTNBF1zk3sksWb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4f26a720\" data-ef-url=\"htt